      "writtenOn": "2018-02-16T17:58:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Another instance of \"Is the sRGB encoding of the dstSurface relevant? (Trying to figure out if you can end up with a srcColorType that\u0027s not possible to combine with the sRGB-ness of the dstSurface).\"",
      "revId": "1dfd6827aa34f1573d693b54a8793c1996d4d78b",
