      "writtenOn": "2018-02-16T19:42:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "To elaborate a bit: fReadColorType is what the caller should pass to GrGpu::readPixels() after doing the temp draw. GrGpu::readPixels() doesn\u0027t have a notion of srgb-ness of the dst buffer. It does type (float/unorm) conversions substitutes 0/1 for missing channels in the src and otherwise preserves values. Similar for GrGpu::writePixels().",
